text: "Warwick Avenue" is a 2008 song by Welsh singer Duffy and is the second single from her debut studio album Rockferry. It went to number 3 in the United Kingdom, number 9 in Scotland and the Netherlands, number 15 in New Zealand and the Netherlands, number 7 in Scotland and Denmark, number 21 in Italy and number 11 in Ireland. ==Formats and track listings== UK CD single #"Warwick Avenue" #"Put It in Perspective" UK 7" vinyl single #"Warwick Avenue" #"Loving You" Australian digital download single #"Warwick Avenue" #"Put It in Perspective" #"Loving You" German maxi single #"Warwick Avenue" #"Put It in Perspective" #"Loving You" #"Warwick Avenue Video" iTunes B-side single #"Put It in Perspective" #"Loving You" Category:2008 songs Category:2000s ballads Category:Rock ballads Category:Soul ballads
